name: Millennials
description:
Game made for Extra Credits Game Jam 4.

Sadly i had only 2 free days for it. A lot of stuff just left for later updates. 

Almost had no time to test 2 player modes properly, waiting for your feeback :)

Additional content will be added after Game Jam Result finals.

In plans:

• Coop campaign

• Mobile support

• Dank memes
